Lunarpine wasn't threatened by this new aquaintance, he knew his new form
could easily overpower her but he'd leave the fighting for the predacons.
"No I'm not from the Cybertronian Fire, I was protecting this scrapheap for
a while until I found a purpose. I went on long range recon and now I'm
back. Now either walk with me to Ramulus or step aside and let me by."
Lunarpine didn't intend to sound cocky but he had business to attend to and
wasn't in the mood for the witty game of 20 questions.
